      <tr>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Accessibility</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">
        <p>Updated guidance on <a href="/accessibility/content#provide-informative-page-titles">providing informative page titles and using headings correctly</a></p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Content guide</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">
        <p>Updated guidance on <a href="/content/pdfs-and-other-non-html-documents">PDFs and other non-HTML documents</a> to mention WCAG 2.2</p>
          <p>Added new guidance about <a href="/content/formatting#headings">headings on Formatting page</a></p>
          <p>Split up <a href="/content/formatting">Formatting</a> and <a href="/content/punctuation">Punctuation</a> sections and added Links guidance to Formatting page</p>
          <p>Added new entries to the A to Z of NHS health writing for:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#ear-drop-and-words-like-eardrum-and-earlobe">ear drop and words like eardrum and earlobe</a></li>
            <li><a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#eye-drop-and-words-like-eyelash-and-eyelid">eye drop and words like eyelash and eyelid</a></li>
            <li><a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#incontinence-products">incontinence products</a></li>
            <li><a href="/content/a-to-z-of-nhs-health-writing#log-in-and-log-out">log in and log out</a></li>
          </ul>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Design system</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">
        <p>Added new <a href="/design-system/components/panel">panel component</a> and <a href="/design-system/patterns/confirmation-page">confirmation page pattern</a></p>
        <p>Added new guidance on <a href="/design-system/styles/page-template#page-title">page titles on Page template page</a></p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
 


